  25:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  26:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****                         ##### How to use this driver #####
  27:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  28:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   [..]
  29:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_ConfigSupply() function to configure the regulator supply
  30:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        with the following different setups according to hardware:
  31:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_SMPS_SUPPLY
  32:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_EXTERNAL_SOURCE_SUPPLY
  33:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  34:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_GetSupplyConfig() function to get the current supply setup.
  35:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  36:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_ControlVoltageScaling() function to configure the main
  37:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        internal regulator output voltage. The voltage scaling could be one of
  38:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        the following scales :
  39:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_REGULATOR_VOLTAGE_SCALE0
  40:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_REGULATOR_VOLTAGE_SCALE1
  41:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  42:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_GetVoltageRange() function to get the current output
  43:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        voltage applied to the main regulator.
  44:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  45:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_ControlStopModeVoltageScaling() function to configure the main
  46:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        internal regulator output voltage in STOP mode. The voltage scaling could be one of
  47:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        the following scales :
  48:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_REGULATOR_STOP_VOLTAGE_SCALE3
  49:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_REGULATOR_STOP_VOLTAGE_SCALE5
  50:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  51:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_GetStopModeVoltageRange() function to get the current output
  52:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        voltage applied to the main regulator in STOP mode.
  53:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  54:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableWakeUpPin() functions to enable the Wake-up pin
  55:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functionality for the selected pin.
  56:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  57:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableBkupRAMRetention() and HAL_PWREx_DisableBkupRAMRetention()
  58:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable BKPSRAM retention in Standby mode.
  59:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  60:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableTCMRetention() and HAL_PWREx_DisableTCMRetention() functions
  61:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        to enable and disable the I-TCM and D-TCM RAMs retention in Standby mode.
  62:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  63:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableTCMFLXRetention() and HAL_PWREx_DisableTCMFLXRetention()
  64:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the I-TCM FLEXMEM retention in Standby mode.
  65:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  66:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_SetPulseLow() function to configure the minimum guaranteed
  67:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        duration of the pwr_on low pulse in Standby mode ( between ~ 0 -> 31 ms).
  68:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  69:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_GetPulseLow() function to get the minimum guaranteed
  70:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        duration of the pwr_on low pulse in Standby mode.
  71:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  72:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableTCMFLXRetention() and HAL_PWREx_DisableTCMFLXRetention()
  73:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the I-TCM FLEXMEM retention in Standby mode.
  74:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  75:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableSMPSPWM() and HAL_PWREx_DisableSMPSPWM() functions to
  76:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        enable and disable the SMPS low-power mode in Stop SVOS range 3.
  77:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  78:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnablePullDownOutput() and HAL_PWREx_DisablePullDownOutput()
  79:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the pull down on output voltage during
  80:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        power-down mode.
  81:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccb319AI.s 			page 3


  82:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableMonitoring() and HAL_PWREx_DisableMonitoring()
  83:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the VBAT and Temperature monitoring.
  84:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        When VBAT and Temperature monitoring feature is enables, use
  85:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        HAL_PWREx_GetTemperatureLevel() and HAL_PWREx_GetVBATLevel() to get
  86:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        respectively the Temperature level and VBAT level.
  87:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  88:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableVDDCOREMonitoring() and HAL_PWREx_EnableVDDCOREMonitoring()
  89:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the VCORE monitoring.
  90:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        When VDDCORE monitoring feature is enables, use HAL_PWREx_GetVDDCORELevel()
  91:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        function to get the current VDDCORE level.
  92:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  93:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_ConfigVDDCORELevel() function to configure the VDDCORE
  94:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        voltage detector low-level selection.
  95:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  96:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_ConfigVddIORange() functions to configure the Vdd IO range:
  97:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_VDDIO
  98:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_VDDIO2
  99:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_VDDIO3
 100:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_VDDIO4
 101:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_VDDIO5
 102:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        The voltage range setting could be one of the following values:
 103:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_VDDIO_RANGE_3V3
 104:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) PWR_VDDIO_RANGE_1V8
 105:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 106:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_GetVddIORange() function to get the current
 107:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        voltage range setting on the selected Vdd IO.
 108:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 109:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableVddIO4RangeSTBY() and HAL_PWREx_DisableVddIO4RangeSTBY()
 110:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the VDD IO4 voltage range Standby mode.
 111:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 112:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableVddIO5RangeSTBY() and HAL_PWREx_DisableVddIO5RangeSTBY()
 113:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the VDD IO5 voltage range Standby mode.
 114:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 115:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableVddUSB() and HAL_PWREx_DisableVddUSB()
 116:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the VDD33USB supply valid.
 117:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 118:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableVddIO2() and HAL_PWREx_DisableVddIO2()
 119:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the VDDIO2 supply valid.
 120:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 121:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableVddIO3() and HAL_PWREx_DisableVddIO3()
 122:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the VDDIO3 supply valid.
 123:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 124:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableVddIO4() and HAL_PWREx_DisableVddIO4()
 125:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the VDDIO4 supply valid.
 126:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 127:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableVddIO5() and HAL_PWREx_DisableVddIO5()
 128:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the VDDIO5 supply valid.
 129:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 130:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableVddA() and HAL_PWREx_DisableVddA()
 131:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        functions to enable and disable the VDDA18ADC supply valid.
 132:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 133:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_ConfigPVM() after setting parameters to be configured
 134:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (event mode and PVD type) in order to set up the Peripheral Voltage
 135:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        Monitor, then use HAL_PWREx_EnableVddUSBVMEN(), HAL_PWREx_EnableVddIO2VMEN(),
