 633:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** /** @defgroup PWREx_Exported_Functions_Group5 Power Monitoring functions
 634:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @brief    Power Monitoring functions
 635:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *
 636:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** @verbatim
 637:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****  ===============================================================================
 638:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****                  ##### Power Monitoring functions #####
 639:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****  ===============================================================================
 640:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 641:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****     *** VBAT and Temperature supervision ***
 642:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****     ========================================
 643:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****     [..]
 644:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       (+) The VBAT battery voltage supply can be monitored by comparing it with
 645:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           two threshold levels: VBAThigh and VBATlow. VBATH flag and VBATL flags
 646:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           in the PWR control register 2 (PWR_BDCR1), indicate if VBAT is higher or
 647:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           lower than the threshold.
 648:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       (+) The temperature can be monitored by comparing it with two threshold
 649:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           levels, TEMPhigh and TEMPlow. TEMPH and TEMPL flags, in the PWR
 650:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           control register 2 (PWR_BDCR1), indicate whether the device temperature
 651:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           is higher or lower than the threshold.
 652:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       (+) The VBAT and the temperature monitoring is enabled by
 653:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           HAL_PWREx_EnableMonitoring() function and disabled by
 654:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           HAL_PWREx_DisableMonitoring() function.
 655:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       (+) The HAL_PWREx_GetVBATLevel() function returns the VBAT level which can
 656:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           be : PWR_VBAT_BELOW_LOW_THRESHOLD or PWR_VBAT_ABOVE_HIGH_THRESHOLD or
 657:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           PWR_VBAT_BETWEEN_HIGH_LOW_THRESHOLD.
 658:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       (+) The HAL_PWREx_GetTemperatureLevel() function returns the Temperature
 659:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           level which can be :
 660:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           PWR_TEMP_BELOW_LOW_THRESHOLD or PWR_TEMP_ABOVE_HIGH_THRESHOLD or
 661:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           PWR_TEMP_BETWEEN_HIGH_LOW_THRESHOLD.
 662:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 663:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** @endverbatim
 664:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @{
